textBeforeTable: Size: φ6.3×5.0L～φ10×11.5L Capacitance: 100～1,600 μF Voltage: 2 V～16 V Endurance: 105°C, 5,000h Highly-reliable power supply Digital equipment (Computers, servers, etc.) Features Applications United Chemi-Con’s PSF series lead-type conductive polymer aluminum solid capacitors are ideally suited to use in computer as VRM bulk capacitors, as well as for noise absorption of DC/DC converters and other applications. We have newly added to the PSF series a product that features large capacitance of 1,200 μF at 2.5 V, while keeping an ESR of 5 mΩ. This will contribute in reducing the number of VRM bulk capacitors used in PC, which will take up less space of the substrate. It is also suitable for use in power supply outputs for noise absorption.
